tgt: leave bedroom and head straight through kitchen, go through the door and stop on porch facing parking area.

src: walk into closet turn then by poster on wall
tgt: Walk into the closet and turn left, then stop and wait by the poster on the wall.

src: through closet turn
tgt: go through closet, turn left.

src: down hallway curved reception desk hall past pots on ground stop near open glass door ways
tgt: Walk down the hallway passed the curved reception desk. Continue down the hall past the pots on the ground and stop near the open glass door ways.

src: along right side of desk pots before glass doors
tgt: Go along the right side of the desk, passed the pots, and stop before the glass doors.

src: down hallway past front desk in between pots by glass doors
tgt: walk down the hallway past the front desk in between the pots and stop by the glass doors.

src: exit bedroom walk through double doors at other end of living room wait in doorway next elephant picture
tgt: Exit the bedroom and walk through double doors at the other end of the living room. Wait in the doorway next to the elephant picture.

src: turn walk across bed exit room with door right left walk towards black chairs wait there
tgt: Turn left walk across the bed and exit the room with the door to the right. Turn left and walk towards two black chairs and wait there.

src: walk in front of bed through archway turn hallway reading nook right with fireplace wait
tgt: Walk in front of the bed and through an archway, turn left down a hallway, to a reading nook to the right with a fireplace and wait.

src: exit room with desks turn toward exit sign wait there
tgt: Exit room with desks. Turn left. Go toward Exit sign. Wait there.

src: walk out into hallway turn walk just past first exit sign on right wall
tgt: Walk out into the hallway. Turn left, and walk just past the first exit sign on the right wall.

src: step forward turn forward then under red exit sign
tgt: Step forward, turn left, move forward, then stop under the red exit sign.

src: turn around up stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Turn around and walk up the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: turn staircase at top of stairs forward before outside
tgt: Turn around and go up the staircase. At the top of the stairs go forward and stop before going outside.

src: stairs in front of door outside
tgt: Go up the stairs and stop in front of the door going outside.

src: stairs turn wait in front of glass doors
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn left. Wait in front of the sliding glass doors.

src: stairs turn at bottom straight towards glass door wait here
tgt: Walk down stairs.  Turn left at the bottom, and walk straight towards sliding glass door.  Wait here.

src: staircase left next open glass door
tgt: Go down the staircase and go left. Stop next to the open glass door.

src: turn room through open door great room wait near stairs on right
tgt: Turn left and exit the room through the open door.  Enter the great room wait near the stairs on your right.

src: turn right then hallway right stairs bench near archway on left
tgt: Turn around and go to the right. Then enter the hallway and turn right to go passed the stairs and the bench. Stop near the archway on the left.

src: bathroom bedroom first into bathroom in front of sink
tgt: Leave the bathroom and bedroom. Take the first left into the bathroom. Stop in front of the sink.

src: walk top of stairs in first across from stairs on right hand side of stairs
tgt: Walk to the top of the stairs, stop in you first doorway across from the stairs on the right hand side of the stairs.

src: walk way up stairs bedroom
tgt: Walk all the way up the stairs and enter the bedroom.

src: up stairs landing stairs second floor right by bedroom door
tgt: walk up the stairs to the landing. continue up the stairs to the second floor. Turn right and stop by the bedroom door.

src: down hall past stairs end of railing right stand in doorway of room at end
tgt: Walk down the hall past the stairs to the end of the railing. Turn right and go stand in the doorway of the room at the end.

src: walk way bedroom doors then tight very corner room right outside door
tgt: Walk straight all the way passing two bedroom doors and then turn tight to enter the very corner room and stop right outside the door.

src: exit bedroom hall wait in doorway living room
tgt: Exit the bedroom, go down the hall and wait in the doorway to the living room.

src: room straight once white frosted glass partition
tgt: Leave the room, and go straight. Stop once you pass the white and frosted glass partition.

src: walk out of home theater turn into living room turn left just inside kitchen
tgt: Walk out of the home theater and turn left. Walk into the living room and turn left. Turn left and stop just inside the kitchen.

src: steps of stairs
tgt: Go up eight steps of the stairs.

src: head first flight of stairs at landing in front of second flight of stairs
tgt: Head up the first flight of stairs.  Stop at the landing in front of the second flight of stairs.

src: up stairs first landing wait there by banister
tgt: Walk up the stairs to the first landing and wait there, by the banister.

src: walk out of storage room into utility room out of door on right down hallway past chairs into kitchen wait there
tgt: Walk out of storage room into utility room. Walk out of door on right. Walk down hallway past three chairs and turn left into kitchen. Wait there.

src: exit storage room adjacent storage room right into hall slight right hallway at end of hall turn kitchen stop at counter on right
tgt: exit storage room to adjacent storage room, turn right into hall, continue slight right down hallway, at end of hall turn left entering kitchen, stop at counter on right.

src: turn across room exit large double wood doors once outside of room
tgt: Turn around and go across the room and exit the large double wood doors. Stop once you are outside of the room.

src: exit room just outside door in hallway next lamp on wall
tgt: Exit the room and stop just outside the door in the hallway, next to the lamp on the wall.
